data.description:
14 MONTH BUYER HOME WARRANTY WITH FULL PRICE OFFER!!  
3 bedroom/ 1 bath cute newly remodeled house for sale with almost a half acre lot!!!  Roof is 7 years old, HVAC, all new plumbing, and water heater within the last two years.  Also the bathroom was completely remodeled down to the studs....new modern updates including bluetooth bathroom exhaust fan.  Smart thermostat included and security camera system can be negotiated.  Fresh paint and floors recently as well!  Has an unfinished mudroom between the backside of the house and the attached garage but the yard is big enough to build a new dream garage!!  Call for a showing today/1!!
